    <h2>1) User accounts, sign up & facebook</h2>

    <h3>1.1 Signing in to Climbfind</h3>

    <p>You can sign in to Climbfind with your Facebook account or with an email address and a password. You can use either method at any time, 
    Climbfind will remember your settings no matter which method you use to sign in.</p>

    <h3>1.2 Advantages of signing in with Facebook</h3>
    
    <p>By using facebook to sign in, you no longer need to type your email address or remember your Climbfind password every time you sign
    into Climbfind. You will also have the option to share your activities on Climbfind directly to your facebook profile.</p>

    <h3>1.3 Connecting your Climbfind account with your Facebook account</h3>
    
    <p>Connecting your accounts is straight forward IF your climbfind account email address is the same as your facebook account email address.
    Simply sign in  to Climbfind with facebook and Climbfind will prompt you to connect your accounts.</p>
    <p>If your email addresses are different, you will not be able to connect your accounts. Either create a new account, or if you have
    a lot of data that you wish to keep on your Climbfind profile, please write in to us at contact@climbfind.com and we will change
    the email address for you.</p>
    
    @*<h3>1.1a Verifying your email address</h3>

    <p>If you have sent yourself a test email and it has not shown up in your inbox, please check your SPAM folder. If you find it in your 
    SPAM folder, mark all mail from Climbfind as "Not Spam". Also add "mailman@climbfind.com" to your contacts / safe list. Please note that 
    sometimes emails take a while to arrive, especially with Yahoo! where emails can take up to 24 hours to appear in your inbox.</p>*@

    <h3>1.4 Forgotten password</h3>

    <p>If you forget you password please <a href="https://accounts.climbfind.com/signin">sign in using Facebook</a> to regain access to your account.
    If your facebook and Climbfind emails are different, you can contact us at contact@climbfind.com and we will reset your password, 
    however we prefer you link your accounts so that you do not lock yourself out again in the future.</p>
            
